&lt;h2 id="tramway">Tramway
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://dartmoorwalking.org/p/meldon-and-the-west-okemont-valley/4.jpg"
width="1600"
height="900"
srcset="https://dartmoorwalking.org/p/meldon-and-the-west-okemont-valley/4_hu_90f7650569827d1e.jpg 480w, https://dartmoorwalking.org/p/meldon-and-the-west-okemont-valley/4_hu_37c1c4b8ddff33a2.jpg 1024w"
